{"tid":277930,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★2017-18 公屋供應急跌25%！未來更越來越少！","createTime":"2017-06-10T04:57:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-10T13:06:09.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a905c792b33d17ca23ed10e0cdf6d35aab4c2f0d","tid":277930,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T04:57:36.000Z","msg":"房屋供應是本屆政府重中之重，特首早前更自詡「政績滯後」，預告今年起大量房屋供應將持續湧現。不過，實情是公屋平均輪候時間直逼五年，一七/一八年度可供編配公屋單位更較去年大減兩成半，只有逾二萬五千個單位，供應量屬十年來第三低；當中逾五成六更靠翻新公屋單位填氹，新單位僅一萬一千餘伙。公屋聯會總幹事招國偉批評政府加建公屋說法不盡不實，直言<span style=\"color: red;\">未來四年不容樂觀，年均只有約一萬四千個新單位</span>，相信公屋輪候時間必拾級上升，短期內勢破五年，敦促政府從速推出新猷，包括提供租金津貼等解基層燃眉之急。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20170610/00174_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170610%2F00174_001.html&d=I2c5v6%2BUs4GnJ2gdj2U%2BBdU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=1f3230e4\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20170610/00174_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a952aa623fadd56bc3209a6a46587ede9eb8b0ac","tid":277930,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T04:58:28.000Z","msg":"突大利好消息<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ccc294f8b2c20b62722e438c37cb02db5b6b03c","tid":277930,"uid":1900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T05:02:07.000Z","msg":"又話有有好多供應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n屌你  樓價又升啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"963b2e05ac440295786ed1c8b7e7f2c157aa49c4","tid":277930,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T05:05:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>突大利好消息<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"